Subject: [PATCH] btrfs: delay blkdev_put until after the device remove
References: bsc#1012628
Patch-mainline: 5.14.8
Git-commit: 3fa421dedbc82f985f030c5a6480ea2d784334c3

[ Upstream commit 3fa421dedbc82f985f030c5a6480ea2d784334c3 ]

